## Data Exploration

```{r}
#| echo: false
#| warning: false

clean |> 
ggplot(mapping = aes(x = D0Fed2TxGrp, y = Result8hrgL, color=D0Fed2TxGrp)) +
  theme_classic()+
  geom_boxplot(outlier.shape=NA) +
  geom_jitter() +
  labs(x = "Second Feeding Treatment", 
       y = "Serum IgG at 8 hrs", 
       title = "Boxplot of Treatment vs. IgG at 8 hours")




```
